name: Jet Ski!
description:
Welcome to Jet Ski!

WARNING: this game is addicting...

Simply tap to change direction of the Jet Ski, and when you are ready, fly as high as you can go -- We Don't Have A Limit For Going UP!!!

When You Go Down It Can Be Quiet Boring So You Only Touch The Bottom Of The Ocean Floor, But You Can Fly As HIGH As You Can... How High Can You Go?

We hope that you enjoy the game =)
